OL,3,CJury retires in trial of police
OL,4,Cmarksman over fatal shooting of Chris
OL,5,CKaba
OL,7,FJurors in the trial of a police
OL,8,Fmarksman accused of the murder of
OL,9,FChris Kaba have retired to consider
OL,10,Ftheir verdicts.
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police firearms officer
OL,13,FMartyn Blake, 40, fatally shot the 24-
OL,14,Fyear-old through the windscreen of an
OL,15,FAudi Q8 in Streatham, south London, on
OL,16,FSeptember 5 2022.
OL,18,FHemmed in by marked and unmarked
OL,19,Fpolice cars, Mr Kaba drove the Audi
OL,20,Fbackwards and forwards in an attempt
OL,21,Fto escape, the Old Bailey has heard.
