OL,3,CJury retires in trial of police
OL,4,Cmarksman over fatal shooting of Chris
OL,5,CKaba
OL,7,FThe car had been used as a getaway
OL,8,Fvehicle in a shooting in nearby
OL,9,FBrixton the night before, and was
OL,10,Ffollowed when a police officer
OL,11,Frecognised the number plate.
OL,13,FOfficers did not know who was driving
OL,14,Fthe car at the time.
OL,16,FThe jury of nine men and three women
OL,17,Fwas told by prosecutor Tom Little KC
OL,18,Fthat Blake had misjudged the risk to
OL,19,Fhis colleagues, and had aimed for Mr
OL,20,FKaba's head when taking the fatal shot.
