OL,5,CKaba
OL,7,FThe prosecution claims the officer
OL,8,Fexaggerated the threat in statements
OL,9,Ffollowing the shooting, incorrectly
OL,10,Fstating that the Audi had been driven
OL,11,Ftowards him and a colleague.
OL,13,FBlake said the driver of an unmarked
OL,14,Fpolice Volvo could have been killed
OL,15,Fwhen the Audi reversed into it at
OL,16,F8mph, which prosecutors said was "a
OL,17,Fgross exaggeration".
