OL,5,CKaba
OL,7,FAnother, NX109, got the finger of his
OL,8,Fglove caught in the Audi's door handle
OL,9,Fand just managed to wrench it free as
OL,10,Fit moved forward, telling the jury he
OL,11,Fthought he would be dragged between it
OL,12,Fand a Tesla parked nearby.
OL,14,FThe jury retired at 11.45am on Monday.
